        {
            "name": "Level 3: Twilight Sanctuary",
            "source": "AliFosche",
            "className": "Cleric",
            "classSource": "XPHB",
            "subclassShortName": "Twilight",
            "subclassSource": "AliFosche",
            "level": 3,
            "entries": [
                "As a Magic Action, you present your holy symbol and emanate a sphere of twilight. The sphere is a 30-foot radius emanation filled with dim light. It moves with you, and lasts for 1 minute or until you are {@condition incapacitated}. Whenever a creature ends its turn within the area, you can grant that creature temporary hit points equal to {@dice 1d6} + your Proficiency Bonus."
            ]
