            "entries": [
                "When you don a suit of armor you can transform it into your Arcane Armor. You gain the following benefits while wearing this armor.",
                {
                    "type": "list",
                    "items": [
                        "You ignore the armor’s Strength requirement.",
                        "You can don or doff the armor as a {@action Utilize} action. The armor can't be removed against your will.",
